WEBVTT

00:05:58.963 --> 00:06:01.597
led to the end of large-scale whaling

00:06:01.630 --> 00:06:05.097
and prevented several
whale species from extinction

00:06:05.130 --> 00:06:08.263
just by showing that whales sing.

00:06:08.297 --> 00:06:10.763
Imagine if we could understand
what they're saying.

00:06:10.797 --> 00:06:14.430
Now is the time
to open this larger dialogue.

00:06:14.463 --> 00:06:17.097
Now is the time to listen deeply

00:06:17.130 --> 00:06:19.030
and show these magical animals,

00:06:19.030 --> 00:06:20.897
and each other,

00:06:20.930 --> 00:06:22.297
newfound respect.

00:06:23.430 --> 00:06:24.663
Thank you.